OL,5, A university professor in Afghanistan  
OL,6, who is an outspoken critic of the      
OL,7, Taliban's ban on education for women   
OL,8, and girls has been arrested in Kabul.  
OL,10,FProf Ismail Mashal was detained on     
OL,11,FThursday while handing out free books. 
OL,13,FHe rose to prominence after he tore up 
OL,14,Fhis academic records live on television
OL,15,Fin protest against the Taliban's ban on
OL,16,Funiversity and secondary school        
OL,17,Feducation for women and girls.         
OL,19,FProf Mashal, 37, has been accused of   
OL,20,F"provocative actions" by the Taliban.  
